        <h1>Hello World!</h1>
        <p>
            My name is Shante Shannon. I was born in Queens, NY, raised in Baltimore, MD and currently reside in a small town called Statesville, North Carolina.
             I am a mother of four: my oldest will be 16 in June, followed by my nine year old and then I have 3 year old boy/girl twins. It is definitely safe to say there is never a dull moment in my household.
             In my downtime, when the house is finally settled I love to get lost in a good book or just listen to music.
             My first memories of using computers started very early in life due to attending a private headstart in Queens where we played mostly educational games; however, I got more into technology in mmiddle school as it started advancing and fell in love with coding during my Myspace high school days.
        </p>
